it.ozimov.cirneco.hamcrest.guava

Class GuavaMatchers

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.ozimov.cirneco.hamcrest.guava.GuavaMatchers

  • public class GuavaMatchers
extends Object
    The GuavaMatchers class groups all the matchers introduced by Cirneco's Hamcrest extension for Google Guava library. Suggested use would be to import all the static methods of this class in a unit test.
    Since:
    version 0.1 for JDK7
